            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "`insert_final_newline = false` means the editor is supposed to ensure the file doesn't end with a newline (see spec at https://spec.editorconfig.org/#supported-pairs).\r\n\r\nneovim is correctly removing the `\\n` at the end of the file.",
