            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Native support for editorconfig is brand new.\r\n\r\nLooking at editorconfig-vim (https://github.com/editorconfig/editorconfig-vim/blob/30ddc057f71287c3ac2beca876e7ae6d5abe26a0/plugin/editorconfig.vim#L461-L473), they're not doing the same thing as neovim.\r\n\r\nAnd it appears that my interpretation of the spec is incorrect: https://github.com/editorconfig/editorconfig/issues/475 leads me to think that the spec is poorly worded and the behavior of editorconfig-vim is the correct one.\r\n\r\nThere's an issue in editorconfig-vim too: https://github.com/editorconfig/editorconfig-vim/issues/136",
